In 2020, China banned all effeminate man in the entertainment industry in order to promote Chinese masculinity. Also, in recent years, China have been banning LGBT clubs, and jailing homoerotic novelists. For the longest time, Taiwan has been muted by the international community due to China, but in recent years, the world has finally taken notice of China’s aggression and threats. We believe this is the best time to tell our side of the story. “Tough Bobas” is seeing the China problems from Taiwanese eyes, because only Taiwan knows the most about China. (And when Taiwanese make fun of issues in China, it’s still politically correct.)
